WEBVTT

00:01:28.078 --> 00:01:30.930
qanday rodda ekanligini bilgan holda 
qo'llash zarur edi.

00:01:30.930 --> 00:01:33.015
Bugungi kunda o'nlab ko'plik anglatuvchi

00:01:33.015 --> 00:01:34.083
g'alati so'zlar bor:

00:01:34.083 --> 00:01:34.769
'men',

00:01:34.769 --> 00:01:35.570
'geese'.

00:01:35.570 --> 00:01:37.578
Oldinlari esa barcha sanoqsiz otlar

00:01:37.578 --> 00:01:40.150
ko'plikni shu kabi so'zlar bilan 
ifodalagan.

00:01:40.150 --> 00:01:43.021
Bitta g'oz - 'goose', bir nechtasi
'geese' ekani g'alatimi?

00:01:43.021 --> 00:01:44.868
Tasavvur qiling, bitta echki — 'goat',

00:01:44.868 --> 00:01:46.489
ko'pi — 'gat',

00:01:46.489 --> 00:01:48.199
bitta eman daraxti — 'oak',

00:01:48.199 --> 00:01:50.283
ko'pi — 'ack'.

00:01:50.283 --> 00:01:52.076
Siz oxiriga -s qo'sha olmasdingiz,

00:01:52.076 --> 00:01:54.850
nutqda ularni qo'llash uchun esa

00:01:54.850 --> 00:01:57.799
ularning ko'plik shaklini bilish 
kerak bo'lardi.

00:01:58.629 --> 00:02:01.261
Ko'plik shaklini yasashda eski